Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_reg_engine_storage#

Notes: The PKO has 40KB of local storage, consisting of 20, 2KB chunks. Up to 15 contiguous chunks may be mapped per engine. The total of all mapped storage must not exceed 40KB.
